# Local PMTiles archives are too large for git (e.g. india.pmtiles ~4.9 GB).
# Ignore everything in public/data/ by default; un-ignore the bundled
# world-low-zoom archive (43 MB) so it ships via Git LFS for the GH Pages
# build. Production self-host volume-mounts at /data/*.pmtiles independently.
public/data/*
!public/data/world-low-zoom.pmtiles
